videos.description: Josh Okogie passes off to Ben Lammers for the two-handed dunk to extend Georgia Tech's early lead over Florida State.
videos.headline: Lammers powers in for two-handed slam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Ben Lammers attacks the lane and dunks over Florida State's Chris Koumadje.
videos.headline: Lammers posterizes FSU defender

videos.description: Off a contested rebound, Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie sprints toward his bucket to finish with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Okogie speeds past FSU D for one-handed slam

videos.description: Josh Heath gives to a slashing Josh Okogie, who finishes with a two-handed dunk in Georgia Tech's 78-56 upset of Florida State.
videos.headline: Heath's pass sets up Okogie's slam in Georgia Tech's upset of FSU

videos.description: In transition, Josh Heath tosses a long pass to Ben Lammers, who catches and dunks it in.
videos.headline: Heath lobs up to Lammers for a dunk
